Revision history for Perl module File::JSON::Slurper

1.00 2020-11-18 NEILB
    - Fixed bug where we were double-encoding. We now assume/require UTF-8.
      Thanks to Dan Book.
      This is a breaking change, so bumped major version.

0.03 2017-08-16 NEILB
    - Corrected the repository URL in the doc.
      Thanks to Ed Freyfogle (EDF) for the pull request.

0.02 2016-11-26 NEILB
    - Corrected the function name in JSON::Parse, in the SEE ALSO section.
      Thanks to Ben Bullock for pointing out my error.

0.01 2016-10-02 NEILB
    - First release to CPAN

